{"tid":2023689,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［公務員加薪出爐］低層公務員加薪1.15% 中為1.98% 高為1.68","createTime":"2020-05-19T07:06:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T07:32:26.000Z","uid":2547,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ac20142e95c8dfd9f2405a6f9aaf66299bf993ef","tid":2023689,"uid":2547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T07:06:46.000Z","msg":"薪酬趨勢調查委員會向公務員簡介今年加薪淨指標，消息指，低級公務員加幅1.15%、中級是1.98%、高級是1.68%。<br />\n<br />\n三個淨指標是分別以薪酬趨勢調查得出的總指標，扣減遞增薪額開支後而得出，薪酬趨勢調查委員會向多個公務員工會及評議會交代有關結果，之後才確認最後向政府遞交的加薪建議。<br />\n<br />\n根據慣例，中低級公務員加薪幅度一般會看齊，若建議獲得通過，加幅將劃一為1.98%，高級公務員加幅為1.68%<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1527030-20200519.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1527030-20200519.htm&d=lEFZiSwVnaVog3Ki0s%2BD%2F1QmTevdAkBFS5MHro4yyYg%3D&h=0ca3ed6e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1527030-20200519.htm&h=1dd61811\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1527030-20200519.htm</a>"},{"pid":"4f2c979c9b643d32da4eeff91a1f88609c809256","tid":2023689,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T07:32:26.000Z","msg":"加薪根本係誤導<br />\n樓價負擔指數由11年大升至20年<br />\n香港人實質收入應該係10年大跌一半至真<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人工資10年間跌左一半 (以樓市購買力計算)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fssOfS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fssOfS</a>"}]}